# Rankings & Data

## Sources

| Source | Format | Consumer |
|--------|--------|----------|
| `rankings_2026.json` | FantasyPros ECR array | `_applyFantasyProsRankings()` |
| `league_setup.json` | `{ version, teams, trades }` | `applySetup()` |
| Sleeper API | Live JSON | `fetchSleeperLeague()` |

Do not invent parallel player schemas — extend the existing runtime player object.

## FantasyPros row shape

`playerName`, `team`, `position`, `ecrRank`, `tier`, `byeWeek`, `averageRank`

Name matching uses normalized lowercase (strip punctuation).

## Rankings update

Replace `rankings_2026.json`; app cache-busts with `?v=YYYY-MM-DD`. After merge, recalc VORP.
